<ab>Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Kessler, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie im der
                            <expan>czolln<ex>er</ex></expan> bey ew nicht
                            <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt, daz er unser
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> wer, er brecht im
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> des einen briefe
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns, das vor nicht gewönlich
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist.
                        <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen den <expan>czolln<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>unt<ex>er</ex>weisen</expan> wöllet, daz er es halt und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lazz, als das bey ew
                                <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, und sünderlich
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein gelt, als er im
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des czolles <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        geseczt hat, <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> gebe. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
